### 9 - Omba Lipenga    
LIFT UP THE TRUMPET   

  **1.**   
 Omba lipenga, limveke ponse;   
 Yesu adzabweranso!   
 Kondweranitu, yimbani nyimbo;   
 Yesu adzabweranso.

  **CHORUS:**   
Abweranso, abweranso, Yesu adzabweranso! 

  **2.**   
 Lalikirani m’phiri ndi m’dambo;   
 Yesu adzabweranso!   
 Adzadza m’ulemerero wake;   
 Yesu adzabweranso. 

  **3.**   
 Lalikirani m’zinyanja monse;   
 Yesu adzabweranso!   
 Lalikirani ponseponsepo;   
 Yesu adzabweranso.

  **4.**   
 Zivomezi zimanena kuti;   
 Yesu adzabweranso!   
 Namondwe ndi mafunde zinena;   
 Yesu adzabweranso. 

  **5.**   
 Mitundu yakwiya tidziwatu;   
 Yesu adzabweranso!   
 Zizindikiro zakwanitsidwa;   
 Yesu adzabweranso.

### 19 - Akhristu Tiyeni   
ONWARD, CHRISTIAN SOLDIERS!   

  **1.**   
 Akhristu tiyeni! Nkhondo tigwire,   
Yesu Mbuye wathu, Atitsogoza,    
Ona mbuye yekha, Atithandiza;   
Ndi mbendera yake, Tiyitsatira.

  **CHORUS:**   
Akristu tiyeni! Nkhondo tigwire,   
Yesu Mbuye wathu, Atitsogoza.

  **2.**   
 Nkhondo ya Satana, Msanga ithawa,   
Akristu tiyeni, Tidzapambana;   
Mphamvu zake zitha, Yesu titama;   
Yimbani anzathu Nyimbo tikweza.

  **3.**   
 Gulu lalikulu, Adza Akhristu;   
Titsatana nawo, Ana a Mlungu;   
Sitipatukana, Tonse tikhala,   
Ndi mtima umodzi, Timakondana.

  **4.**   
 Zonse za pa dziko, Zidzatheratu;   
Koma mpingo wake, Ukhalitsabe;   
Mphamvu ya Satana, Idzalefuka;   
Yesu nalonjeza Ndidzalimbitsa.

  **5.**   
 Idzani Akhristu, Kutithandiza,   
Nyimbo za Mulungu, Tidzayimbitsa;   
Khristu ayenera, Ndiye Mfumuyo,   
Tidzamlemekeza, Nthawi zonsezo.

### 91 - Linda Ndi Kupemphera    
WATCH, FOR THE TIME IS SHORT   

  **1.**   
 Dikirani lero nthawi ili kutha;   
 Mungagwe m’zoipa linda ndi pemphero;   
 Thupi ndi lofoka mdaniyo ngwa mphamvu;   
 Dikirani nonse Mkwati ali kudza.   


  **CHORUS:**   
 Linda pempha, linda pempha;   
 Usiku ndi usana dikirani ndi kupemphera.   
 (Tenor and Bass)   
 Linda pempha, linda pempha;   
 Linda pempha, linda pempha;   
 Usiku ndi usana dikirani ndi kupemphera.   

  **2.**   
 Dzukani m’sagone musamakaika;   
 Mudzalandiratu mpumulo kumwamba;   
 Linda ndi pemphero, Mpulumutsi wanu,   
 Anasautsidwa chifukwa cha inu   

  **3.**   
 Khulupira Yesu mdani ali pompo   
Vala zida zako mpaka Mbuye adze,   
 Musachedwe konse lero ndi labwino,   
 Dikirani nonse ndi kupempheranso.

### 125 - Muli Dzuwa M’phiri Muja   
SUNLIGHT IN THE HEART   

  **1.**   
 Muli dzuwa m’phiri muja, Muli dzuwa m’nyanjamo;   
 K’wala kwace kumagwera Pa maudzu ponsepo;   
 Koma dzuwa lopambana Liri m’tima mwangamu;   
 Ka’mba komwe mukhalitsa, Kuli dzuwa lowala. 

  **CHORUS:**   
 Muli dzuwa lakuwalitsa! Muli dzulwa m’timanga.   
 Yesu adzacotsa mdima, Muli dzuwa m’timanga.  

  **2.**   
 Ndisiya ’ne nsoni zanga Ndi zobvala za nsanza;   
 Mundibvekatu zoyera, Ndiyamika m’mtimamo’    
 Kuli malo a ulemu Munandikonzera ’ne;   
 Mtima wanga ufunako, Ndizatsa Inutu.   

  **3.**   
 Inu, Yesu, Mwandigula, Ndine wanu konseko,   
 Munayatsa nyali yanga, Iwalire Inuyo;   
 Kuli malo a ulemu Munandikonzera ’ne,   
 Mtima wanga ufunako, Ndidzatsa Inuyo.

### 129 - Yesu Mnalonjeza   
JESUS, COME AND BLESS US   

  **1.**   
 Yesu mnalonjeza, Kuti komwetu   
 Asonkhana ’tatu, Muli komweko;   
 Tikukhulupira, Tigwadira ’Nu;   
 Yesu, mtidalitse, Mkhale nafetu 

  **CHORUS:**   
 Yesu, mtidalitse Popemphera ’fe;   
 Yesu, mtidaliste, Mkhale mfupimo.   

  **2.**   
 Mnasonkhana nafe Nthawi zonsezo,    
 Tikusowaninso Mpaka mapeto;   
 ;Dzani, Mpulumutsi, Mtidalitsenso;   
 Mutimvere ife, Tikupempha ’Nu.   

  **3.**   
 Yesu, mtithangate Poyimbira ’Nu,   
 Pempho liri lonse Mlilandiretu;   
 Cikh’lupiro cathu Mcikulitsenso;   
 Mdzaze ’fe cikondi, Ndi ku’nikanso.

### 133 - Ndiyende Nanu Mulungu    
WALKING WITH GOD   

  **1.**   
 Ndiyende nanu Mlungu ’Nu, Mongatu Enoke kalelo;   
 Mndigwire dzanja langalo, Mulankhule ndi inenso;   
 Ngakhale sindionatu, Ndiyende ndinu, Mbuyanga   

  **2.**   
 Sin’funa Kwenda ndekhatu, Namondwe amaombabe;   
 Misampha indicera ’ne, Adani andizinganso;   
 Mutontholetse njanjayo, Ndiyende ndinu, Mbuyanga.   

  **3.**   
 Mukandigwira dzanjali, Nditayatu za dzikoli;   
 Ndzayenda molimbikatu, Ndzasenza mtanda wangawao;   
 Mpakatu ndzanke m’mwambamo, Ndiyende ndinu, Mbuyanga.

### 153 - Sindipemphera, Mbuyanga   
JUST FOR TO-DAY   

  **1.**   
 Sindipemphera, Mbuyanga, Za mawazo;   
 Mndipulumutse m’chimolo Lero lokha;   
 Mau ndisalankhulenso Oipawo;   
 Msungetu mlomo wangawu, Lero lino.   

  **2.**   
 Ndzagwira ntchito yanuyo, Ndzapemphanso;   
 Ndikhalal wacifundoyo, Lero lokha;   
 Mundithandize, Mbuyanga, Kumera ’Nu;   
 Kuti ndidzipereketu pa leroli.   

  **3.**   
 Ngatitu moyo wangawo Utha ndithu;   
 M’malonjezano anuwo ndikhalebe;   
 Sindipemphera, Mbuyanga, Za mawazo;   
 M’ndisunge m’manja mwanumo pa leroli.

### 161 - Tsamwali Ndiri Naye    
MY LORD AND I   

  **1.**   
 Tsamwali ndiri naye Wolondakondadi;   
 Akonda ’ne koposatu, Akonda konseko;   
 Ndikhala ndi tsamwaliyo, Ndimkonda bwinotu;   
 Pamodzi ndi Ambuye Ndikhalabe.   

  **2.**   
 Ndifo’ka ndithu mwina, Adziwa Mbuyeyo   
 Auza ’ne ndimtsamire, Andithangatatu;   
 Anditsogoza inetu, Mwa kuunikako,   
 Pamodzi ndi Ambuye Ndiyendabe.   

  **3.**   
 Zokondwa, za cisoni, Ndiuza Mbuyeyo;   
 Ndiuza Mbuye zonsetu Za Mtima mwangamo;   
 Auza ’ne cocitatu, Anena, Yesanso;   
 Pamodzi ndi Ambuye Ndinenabe.   

  **4.**   
 Adziwa ndikufuna, Kukopa winayo,   
 Auza ’ne kupitatu Kunena nayenso;   
 Cikondi ca Mulunguyo, Ndi imfa ya Yesu;   
 Pamodzi ndi Ambuye ndicitabe.

### 162 - Yesu Anditsogozatu    
ALL THE WAY   

  **1.**   
 Yesu anditsogozatu; Nanganso ndifunanji?   
 Kodi ndimkaika Iye, Wonditsogolerayo?   
 Mtenderewo andipatsa, Mwa cikhulupiroco!   
 Mkana lindigwere bvuto, Yesu athangata ’ne’   
 Mkana lindigwere bvuto, Yesu athangata ’ne;   

  **2.**   
 Yesu anditsogolera, Andisangalatsanso;   
 Athandiza ’ne m’mayeso, Andidyetsa mkatewo;   
 Nkana ndiri wakutopa, Ludzu landigwiranso,   
 Mu Thanthwelo Yesu Kristu, Ndionamo madziwo;   
 Mu Thanthwelo Yesu Kristu, Ndionamo madziwo;   

  **3.**   
 Yesu anditsogolera, Mwa cikondi caceco!   
 Alonjeza ’ne mpumulo, Mnyumba ya Atateyo;   
 Nkadzauka tsiku lijaa, Ndidzapita mmwambamo,   
 Ndidzayimba kosaleka, Yesu natsogoza ’ne;   
 Ndidzayilmba kosaleka, Yesu natsogoza ’ne;

### 167 - Maziko Olimba    
FIRM FOUNDATION   

  **1.**   
 Maziko olimba Ambuyathuyo, Waikira inutu m’mau mwace,   
 Anene ciani koposa ico? Wathawira ndani kwa Mp’lumutsiyo;   
 Wathawira ndani kwa Mp’lumutsiyo.   

  **2.**   
 Ndikati uyende mitsinjepo, Madziwo sadzakukokolola ’we;   
 Pakuti ndzakhala pamodzi nawe, Ndzadalitsa iwe, ndzapatule ’we;   
 Ndzadalitsa iwe, ndzapatula ’we.   

  **3.**   
 Poyenda ’we m’moto wa mayesowo, Cisomo cangaco cikwaniradi;   
 Sudzapsa konsei ndangofunatu kucotsa zoipa kuyeretsa ’we,   
 Kucotsa zoipa kuyeretsa ’we.   

  **4.**   
 Wakudza kwa Yesu kubisalako, Sindimataya kunjatu kwa mdaniyo;   
 Ngakhale adani amgwedezetu, Sindimsiya konse, sindimsiyatu;   
 Sindimsiya konse, sindimsiyatu.

### 181 - Sitidziwa Kudza Kwa Mbuye    
WAITING AND WATCHING   

  **1.**   
 Sitidziwa kudza kwa Mbuye, Madzulo kapena Mmawa;   
 Kapena nthawi ya usiku, Kapena m’mabinga kuca;   
 Atiuzatu tikonzeke, Tisazime nyali zathu;   
 Pobwera adzatipezetu, Tiri kumdikira Iye 

  **CHORUS:**   
 Kudikiratu, kudikiratu; kucezeratu, Ndi yang’anira Inu. Alto, Tenor, and Bass;   
 Kudikiratu ndi kupemphere, Kudikiratu ndi kupemphera;   
 Kucezeratu ndi kupemphera, Ndi kuyang’anira Inu.   

  **2.**   
 Cikondi cace ncodabwintsa, Kutiombola ifetu;   
 Anasiya malo oposa, Nadza kudzaferatu;   
 Nthaawi zonse amakondwera, Mmene oomboledwawo;   
 Akondwera m’ciyembekezo, Podikira Mbuye wao.   

  **3.**   
 Inu Yesu, Mombolo wanga, Mudziwa ndikukondani,   
 Ndiyembekeza kuniona, Ndizamva mau anuwo;   
 Mmene mudzadza kuweruza, Ena adzakuthawani,   
 Koma ine ndizakondwera, Ndiri kudikira inu.

### 216 - Sindiri Ndekha    
NEVER ALONE   

  **1.**   
 Ndekha? Bi, sindiri ndekha Yesu ngwanga;    
 Amandisangalatsa; ali pafupipa,   
 Ulibe bwenzi ko, Ndiri naye Yesu;   
 Ndimasinthasinthadi, Iye sasinthatu. 

  **CHORUS:**   
 Sindiri ndekha, sindiri ndekha;   
 Anapangana nane kuti sadzandisiya ndekha.   

  **2.**   
 Kutopa? Nditoperenji, Yesu ngwanga;   
 Ndatsamira pa Iye, Ndiri kupumula,   
 Wosowawe; Inde ndatsamira zedi,   
 Pa dzanja lace Yesu phe Andisamalira.   

  **3.**   
 Kulindira? Inde, kulindira;   
 Kaya acedweranji Ambuye kubwera,   
 Ndiye ukukondwa? Inde, kukondwadi;   
 Ndikondwa ndi maziko ndiye Ambuyanga.

### 218 - Maziko Amodzi    
ONE FOUNDATION   

  **1.**   
 Maziko a mpingo amodzi ndi Kristu;   
 Colenga catsopano, mwa madzi ndi mau;   
 Anatsika kumwamba nalenga mpingowo;   
 Naugula ndi mwazi naufera mpingo.   

  **2.**   
 Wokwanira mitundu yonse ya pa dziko;   
 Koma cipulumutso mwa njira imodzi,   
 Dzinali loyeretsa lapanga mpingowu,   
 Cogaawira cimodzi cisomo coyera.   

  **3.**   
 Ponyoza mpingo wace anthu adzaona,   
 Adani apasula Thanthwe sadzalitha;   
 Oyerawo osunga cikhulupiriro;   
 Cisoni cikadzatha, tidzakondwerera.   

  **4.**   
 M’kati mwa masauko a mpingo woyera;   
 Mpingo ulindirira cipulumutsoco;   
 Maso otopa nako kulira kukwera;   
 Mpingo waukuruwo udzagonjetsadi.

### 220 - Kwathu    
THE HOMELAND   

  **1.**   
 Ndilakalaka kwathu! Dziko laufulu!   
 Kwathu kopanda mdima, Kulibe usiku;   
 Ndiri kulira kwathu, Mtima suli bwino;   
 Kulibe z owawa kwathu, Ndayandikirako;   
 Kulibe zowawa kwathu, Ndayandikirako.   

  **2.**   
 Mbuyanga ali kwathu, Angelo abwino;   
 Kulibe chimo kwathu, Mayeso kulibe;   
 Nyimbozo za kwathuko Ndiri kuzimvatu   
 Ndikaganiza za kwathu Ndilira misozi   
 Ndikaganiza za kwathu Ndilira misozi   

  **3.**   
 Anthu okhala kwathu Andikodolane,   
 Kopanda zacisoni Kwa okhala mommo;   
 Komomadi kwathuko! Kwa mtendere uko!   
 Kristu atifitsa kwathu Mwini wotikonda;   
 Kristu atifitsa kwathu Mwini wotikonda.

### 225 - Uyang’ane Mdaniyo    
STAND LIKE THE BRAVE   

  **1.**   
 Mkhristuwe dzuka! Alamula Mbuye;    
 Tenga cikopa, ndi lupanga m’dzanja,   
 Ukomane naye, usamuope   
 Ulimbe Mtima, Myang’ane mdaniyo. Refrain;   
 Limba Mtima, Limba Mtima,   
 Limba Mtima, Pom’yang’ana mdani.   

  **2.**   
 Zoopsa ziripo, ucenjeretu,   
 Usafulatire, ungapwekekwe;   
 Unyinji wa ’dani, udzagonjetsa,   
 Ulimbe Mtima, M’yang’ane mdaniyo.   

  **3.**   
 Ntchito ya Mbuyako uiteteze;   
 Dzukatu mwa cangu nkhondoyo ithe;   
 Akakulamula, pita mwa cangu,   
 Ulimbe Mtima M’yang’ane mdaniyo.   

  **4.**   
 Pita limbikira, suli wekhai,   
 Mwayi apatsa, cisangalatsonso;   
 Mwayi apatsa, cisangalatsonso;   
 Cikondi cace ngati mtsinje m’tengo;   
 Ulimbe Mtima M’yang’ane mdaniyo

### 277 - Tsogolere Muuni   
LEAD KINDLY LIGHT   

  **1.**   
 Tsogolere muuni mu mdima, Tsogolere;   
 Kwada ndiri kutari ndi kwathu; Tsogolere   
 Sindipempha kuona za m’tari,   
 Phazi langa limodzi likwana   

  **2.**   
 Sindinali wotere wokhoza kupemphera;   
 Ndisankha njira’nga; Tsogolere;   
 Ndinakonda zinthu zacibwana, Tsogolere;   
 Ndinanyada, musazikumbuke   

  **3.**   
 Mphamvu yanu yandidalitsadi; Intsogoza   
 Mu malo monse moipa mpaka mdima watha;   
 M’mawa ’ngelo andisekerera;   
 Amenewo ndawakonda kale.

### 284 - Popita Masikuwa   
WHILE THE DAYS ARE GOING BY   

  **1.**   
 Kuli anthu obvutika, Popita masikuwa,   
 Kuli anthu akutopa, Popita masikuwa;   
 Ngati tiwakondwetsa, Poyenda ulendowu   
 Zabwino ticitetu, Popita masikuwa. 

  **CHORUS:**   
 Masiku apita, Masiku apita,   
 Zabwino ticitetu! Popita masikuwa.   

  **2.**   
 Kulibe nthawi yotaya, Popita masikuwa;   
 Mukhale osangalala, Popita masikuwa;   
 Dziko liri m’cisoni, Misozi ndi maliro;   
 Thandiza obvutika, Popita masikuwa.   

  **3.**   
 Zotimanga tizisiya, Popita masikuwa;   
 Modzi ndi mmodzi atsala, Popita masikuwa   
 Zabwino tidzakhala, ponse ponse zimera;   
 Tidzakhala okondwa, Popita masikuwa.

### 313 - Pa Ubatizo   
PRAYER AT BAPTISM   

  **1.**   
 Atate muwapenye Anzathu onsewo;   
 Abvomereza dzina La Yesu Kristuyo;   
 Alonjezetsa lero Kutsata Mbuyeyo,   
 Mwathangatire iwo Asabwererenso.   

  **2.**   
 Onsewa afa ndithu M’zoipa zawozo;   
 Tsopano aikidwa Ndi Kristu m’mandamo;   
 Auke iwo onse Kuyenda nayeyo;   
 Aphe nthawi zonse Ndi kudya mauwo.   

  **3.**   
 Muwalimbitse, Mbuye, Kuyenda m’njirayi,   
 Ndi kugonetsa mdani Masiku onsewo;   
 Muwathangate iwo Kukopa enawo,   
 Amene ali kufa M’zoipa zawozo.
